room_title: Escape room "Spymaker" by Spymaker Escape Rooms in Flint
room_description:
Cut to Europe early 1940’s. A top-secret document was intercepted by enemy spy’s (STOP) Your government has discovered where they are keeping it (STOP) Your Mission; sneak into enemy territory, recover the document, and return it to HQ before time expires.

You have 60 minutes to get the Battle plans back or be captured.
